{
  "name": "Planar Sword",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You create a sword-shaped plane of force that hovers within range. It lasts for the duration.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>When the sword appears, you make a melee spell attack against a target of your choice within 5 feet of the sword. On a hit, the target takes [[/r 3d10]] force damage. Until the spell ends, you can use a bonus action on each of your turns to move the sword up to 20 feet to a spot you can see and repeat this attack against the same target or a different one.</p></div>",
